    h2 
        + Features
    ul 
        li 
            + üåü I18n is an essential part of the user experience, therefore this library doesn&#39;t compromise on flexibility and never leaves you behind when you need to fine tune a translation. Messages use the proven
            a 
                href https://formatjs.io/docs/core-concepts/icu-syntax
                title 
                + ICU syntax
            + which covers interpolation, numbers, dates, times, plurals, ordinal pluralization, label selection based on enums and rich text.
        li 
            + ‚öîÔ∏è Based on battle-tested building blocks from
            a 
                href https://formatjs.io/
                title 
                + Format.JS
            + (used by
            code react-intl
            + ), this library is a thin wrapper around high-quality, lower-level APIs for i18n.
        li 
            + üíØ Built-in number and date formatting that is integrated with translations, e.g. allowing for the usage of global formats for a consistent look &amp; feel of your app.
        li 
            + üí° A hooks-only API ensures that you can use the same API for
            code children
            + as well as for attributes which expect strings.
        li 
            + üöÄ Integrates with both static as well as server side rendering.
